<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Confirm Your Account</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #691f74;
      --primary-color-dark: #44195d; 
      --body-background-color: #f4f4f4;
      --text-color: #333;
      --text-light-color: #666;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Poppins';
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 400;
      src: local('Poppins Regular'), local('Poppins-Regular'), url(https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/poppins/v15/pxiByp8kv8JHgFVrLDz8Z1xlFQ.woff2) format('woff2');
    }
    /* Add your styles here */
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      border: #333;
    }
    .banner {
      background-color: #44195d;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
    }
    a {
      color: #691f74;
    }
    p {
      color: #333;
      opacity: 0.8;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 16px 26px;
      font-weight: 600;
      background-color: #691f74;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 35px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #44195d;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f0e9f1; padding: 40px;">
  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600" style="background-color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border: #333;">
          <tr>
            <td>
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background-color: #44195d; text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: white; border-top-left-radius: 16px; border-top-right-radius: 16px;">
                    <h1>Welcome to Jobster</h1>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 40px;">
                    <h2 style="color: #333;">Confirm Your Account</h2>
                    <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
                    <p>Welcome to Jobster! We're thrilled to have you on board.</br>
                    To get started, please click the button below to confirm your email address:</p>
                    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;">
                          <a href="<%= confirmationURL %>" class="btn" style="color: #fff;">Confirm Account</a>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                    <p>If the button above doesn't work, you can also confirm your account by copying and pasting the following link into your browser:</p>
                    <p><a href="<%= confirmationURL %>" style="color: #691f74;"><%= confirmationURL %></a></p>
                    <p>Thank you for choosing Jobster.</br>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@jobster.com" style="color: #691f74;">support@jobster.com</a></p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
